{"nodes": [{"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegraph_graphify_vs_codegraph", "label": "Graphify vs CodeGraph (decisi\u00f3n de tooling de navegaci\u00f3n del repo)", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/graphify-vs-codegraph.md", "source_location": "t\u00edtulo", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegraph_codegraph", "label": "CodeGraph", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/graphify-vs-codegraph.md", "source_location": "\u00a72 Cara a cara", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Grafo SQLite de s\u00edmbolos (AST): barato (~0 tokens), preciso, latencia sub-ms, daemon en vivo, ya cableado en MCP y CLAUDE.md global. Limitaci\u00f3n decisiva: solo indexa 23 archivos (17 py + 6 yaml) y no ve la prosa, que es el 90 % del repo."}, {"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegraph_graphify", "label": "Graphify", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/graphify-vs-codegraph.md", "source_location": "\u00a72 Cara a cara", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Grafo de conocimiento LLM-asistido: indexa 308 archivos (c\u00f3digo + 237 docs + 2 PDF), 1.682 nodos / 2.378 aristas, ve la prosa y produce puentes entre-documento relevantes. Costes: ~1,6 M tokens por build, snapshot (hay que rehacer), sin integraci\u00f3n MCP. Salvedad: ~212 aristas colgantes (~8 %) por IDs no compartidos entre chunks."}, {"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegraph_estrategia_dual", "label": "Estrategia dual: usar las dos, cada una en su mitad", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/graphify-vs-codegraph.md", "source_location": "TL;DR y \u00a74 Recomendaci\u00f3n", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "No compiten: resuelven problemas distintos sobre un repo que es 90 % prosa (229 md / 33.591 l\u00edneas vs 17 py + 27 sh). CodeGraph como capa por defecto para editar c\u00f3digo (gratis, preciso, ya integrado); Graphify como mapa peri\u00f3dico del corpus de prosa (un build por mes o tras cambios grandes en references/), consultado con graphify query sobre graph.json. Su audit trail EXTRACTED/INFERRED/AMBIGUOUS encaja con la tesis de atribuci\u00f3n del proyecto."}, {"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegraph_politica_versionado_graphify_out", "label": "Pol\u00edtica de versionado de graphify-out/", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/graphify-vs-codegraph.md", "source_location": "\u00a75", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Versionar solo lo que necesit\u00f3 destilaci\u00f3n desde un modelo: cache/semantic/ (239 entradas, ~1,2 M) cost\u00f3 ~1,6 M tokens y es lo \u00fanico no reconstruible gratis; graph.json, graph.html, GRAPH_REPORT.md, cache/ast/ y dem\u00e1s se regeneran determin\u00edsticamente sin LLM. Implementado como allowlist en graphify-out/.gitignore; un rebuild futuro reutiliza la cach\u00e9 (~0 tokens en archivos sin cambios)."}, {"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegraph_cache_semantic", "label": "graphify-out/cache/semantic/ (extracci\u00f3n sem\u00e1ntica versionada)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/graphify-vs-codegraph.md", "source_location": "\u00a75", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegraph_piramide_de_prosa", "label": "Pir\u00e1mide de prosa (tres capas)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/graphify-vs-codegraph.md", "source_location": "\u00a73", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegraph_prosa_base", "label": "prosa-base (capa 1)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/graphify-vs-codegraph.md", "source_location": "\u00a73", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegraph_marcela_prose", "label": "marcela-prose / voz de la autora (capa 3)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/graphify-vs-codegraph.md", "source_location": "\u00a73", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegraph_duplicacion_capa_voz", "label": "Duplicaci\u00f3n de la capa de voz en dos \u00e1rboles", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/graphify-vs-codegraph.md", "source_location": "\u00a73", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Gotcha redescubierto por el grafo: writeonmars/references/voz/ (preset empaquetado) y .claude/skills/marcela-prose/ (skill instalada / dogfooding) espejan los mismos ficheros (arquitectura-capitulo.md, registros-por-modalidad.md) en dos comunidades distintas. Es una superficie de sincronizaci\u00f3n real que CodeGraph no puede producir."}, {"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegraph_claimrecord", "label": "claims.md / ClaimRecord v1.0", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/graphify-vs-codegraph.md", "source_location": "\u00a73", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegraph_citationrecord", "label": "CitationRecord v1.0", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/graphify-vs-codegraph.md", "source_location": "\u00a73", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegraph_gate_g4", "label": "Gate g4 (factualidad)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/graphify-vs-codegraph.md", "source_location": "\u00a73", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegraph_firmas_desviacion_justificada", "label": "Firmas desviaci\u00f3n_justificada (proxy humano)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/graphify-vs-codegraph.md", "source_location": "\u00a73", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_graphify_vs_codegrap